  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV97">
<l>eḻuvatu mīṇṭē paṭuvatum paṭṭeṉai yūḻikaḷpōyk</l>
<l>kaḻivatuṅ kaṇṭukaṇ ṭeṭkalal lālimai yōrkaḷkuḻān</l>
<l>toḻuvatuñ cūḻvatuñ ceytollai mālaikkaṇ ṇārakkaṇṭu</l>
<l>kaḻivatōr kātaluṟ ṟārkkumuṇ ṭōkaṇkaḷ tuñcutalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>those who have a love for</l>
<l>rising and suffering again, passing time in suffering [and] going through however many aeons,</l>
<l>besides being bashful(?), looking [and] looking out, worshipping the throngs of unblinking ones,</l>
<l>cirbumambulating, passing time in looking, to [their] eyes’ fill, at ancient Māl</l>
	<l>– is there sleeping for their eyes?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
